<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200805/b7dfc3f5725440d9b5333d4baaaf8bba.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">明月照高楼</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">流光正徘徊</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">仰望苍穹里</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">招手邀圆月</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200805/093edd4255c44eb591fb5172174817ad.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
